sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Administrator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as RHODS Operator<br/>ServiceAccount Token Auth
    participant GitHub as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>via kube-rbac-proxy
    participant Components as Managed Components

    Note over User,Components: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Component Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: POST DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Auth: User credentials/Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Event: DataScienceCluster created<br/>In-Memory
    Operator->>GitHub: GET /component/manifests<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>No Auth
    GitHub-->>Operator: Return Kustomize manifests
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply component resources<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Components: Deploy components<br/>In-Memory

    Note over User,Components: Flow 2: CRD Conversion Webhook

    User->>K8sAPI: POST legacy API version<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /convert<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS1.2+ mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Converted CR<br/>Response over mTLS
    K8sAPI-->>User: Success response

    Note over User,Components: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Operator: GET /metrics via kube-rbac-proxy<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over Operator: kube-rbac-proxy validates token<br/>then proxies to port 8080
    Operator-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>HTTP response

    Note over User,Components: Flow 4: Platform Initialization (DSCInitialization)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST DSCInitialization CR<br/>Auth: Admin credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Event: DSCInitialization created<br/>In-Memory
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create namespaces<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshControlPlane<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Prometheus/Alertmanager<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: Platform initialized
